统公司、通用动力军械与战术系统公司、通用动力信息技术公司、通用动力任务系统公司、海岸间电子公司、系统研究与模拟公司、铁山解决方案公司、应用技术集团、阿克西恩特公司等12家后附《反制清单》列明的企业，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对凯西·沃登（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司董事长、首席执行官、总裁）、马修·布朗伯格（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司全球运营副总裁）、本杰明·戴维斯（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司战略威慑系统副总裁、总经理）、托马斯·琼斯（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、航空系统总裁）、斯蒂芬·奥布莱恩（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、全球业务发展官）、罗珊·罗德（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、防务系统总裁）、菲拉特·盖曾（通用动力公司副总裁、通用动力军械与战术系统公司总裁）、贾森·艾肯（通用动力公司负责技术部门执行副总裁）、艾米·吉格兰（通用动力公司高级副总裁、通用动力信息技术公司总裁）、克里斯托弗·布雷迪（通用动力公司副总裁、通用动力任务系统公司总裁）等10名后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年5月22日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年5月22日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/7> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"艾米·吉格兰","cn:english_name":"Amy Gilliland"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/anti-sanction-list/7-christopher-j-brady>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/7-christopher-j-brady> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_anti_sanctions> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"visa_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Visa ban and entry prohibition (including Hong Kong and Macao)","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"美国无视中方在乌克兰危机上的客观公正立场和建设性作用，以所谓涉俄罗斯因素为由对多家中国实体滥施非法单边制裁。同时，美国持续向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报规定。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"The US disregards China's objective and fair position and constructive role in the Ukraine crisis, imposing illegal unilateral sanctions on multiple Chinese entities under the pretext of so-called Russia-related factors. Meanwhile, the US continues to sell weapons to China's Taiwan region.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-05-22","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "7-christopher-j-brady" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"关于对美国军工企业及高级管理人员采取反制措施的决定","url":"https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zfxxgk_674865/gknrlb/fzcqdcs/202405/t20240522_11309756.shtml","publish_date":"2024-05-22","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs-order","document_id":"第7号","signatory":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","authority":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","content":"（2024年5月22日中华人民共和国外交部令第7号公布，自2024年5月22日起施行）\n\n一段时间以来，美国无视中方在乌克兰危机上的客观公正立场和建设性作用，以所谓涉俄罗斯因素为由对多家中国实体滥施非法单边制裁，大搞单边霸凌和经济胁迫，严重侵犯中方企业、机构和个人正当合法权益。同时，美国持续向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报规定，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。\n\n依据《中华人民共和国反外国制裁法》第三条、第四条、第五条、第六条、第九条、第十五条规定，中方决定对以下美国军工企业及高级管理人员采取反制措施：\n\n一、对洛克希德·马丁导弹与火控公司、洛克希德·马丁航空公司、标枪合资公司、雷神导弹系统公司、通用动力军械与战术系统公司、通用动力信息技术公司、通用动力任务系统公司、海岸间电子公司、系统研究与模拟公司、铁山解决方案公司、应用技术集团、阿克西恩特公司等12家后附《反制清单》列明的企业，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对凯西·沃登（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司董事长、首席执行官、总裁）、马修·布朗伯格（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司全球运营副总裁）、本杰明·戴维斯（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司战略威慑系统副总裁、总经理）、托马斯·琼斯（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、航空系统总裁）、斯蒂芬·奥布莱恩（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、全球业务发展官）、罗珊·罗德（诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司副总裁、防务系统总裁）、菲拉特·盖曾（通用动力公司副总裁、通用动力军械与战术系统公司总裁）、贾森·艾肯（通用动力公司负责技术部门执行副总裁）、艾米·吉格兰（通用动力公司高级副总裁、通用动力信息技术公司总裁）、克里斯托弗·布雷迪（通用动力公司副总裁、通用动力任务系统公司总裁）等10名后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年5月22日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年5月22日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/7> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"克里斯托弗·布雷迪","cn:english_name":"Christopher J. Brady"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/anti-sanction-list/8-lockheed-martin-missile-system>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/8-lockheed-martin-missile-system> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_anti_sanctions> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"asset_freeze","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Freeze all assets in China, including movable and immovable property and other types of assets","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"The US recently announced again the sale of weapons to China's Taiwan region, seriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US joint communiqués, seriously interfering in China's internal affairs, and seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-06-21","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "8-lockheed-martin-missile-system" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"关于对洛克希德·马丁公司实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施的决定","url":"https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zfxxgk_674865/gknrlb/fzcqdcs/202406/t20240621_11439508.shtml","publish_date":"2024-06-21","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs-order","document_id":"第8号","signatory":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","authority":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","content":"（2024年6月21日中华人民共和国外交部令第8号公布，自2024年6月21日起施行）\n\n美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。依据《中华人民共和国反外国制裁法》第三条、第四条、第五条、第六条、第九条、第十五条规定，中方决定对洛克希德·马丁公司相关实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施：\n\n一、对洛克希德·马丁导弹系统集成实验室、洛克希德·马丁先进技术实验室、洛克希德·马丁风险投资公司等后附《反制清单》列明的实体，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对洛克希德·马丁公司董事长、总裁、首席执行官詹姆斯·泰克里特、首席运营官弗兰克·圣约翰、首席财务官杰西·马莱夫等后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产；禁止我国境内的组织、个人与其本人进行有关交易、合作等活动；不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年6月21日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年6月21日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/8> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"洛克希德·马丁导弹系统集成实验室","cn:english_name":"Lockheed Martin Missile System Integration Lab"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/anti-sanction-list/8-lockheed-martin-advanced-techno>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/8-lockheed-martin-advanced-techno> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_anti_sanctions> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"asset_freeze","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Freeze all assets in China, including movable and immovable property and other types of assets","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"The US recently announced again the sale of weapons to China's Taiwan region, seriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US joint communiqués, seriously interfering in China's internal affairs, and seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-06-21","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "8-lockheed-martin-advanced-techno" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"关于对洛克希德·马丁公司实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施的决定","url":"https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zfxxgk_674865/gknrlb/fzcqdcs/202406/t20240621_11439508.shtml","publish_date":"2024-06-21","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs-order","document_id":"第8号","signatory":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","authority":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","content":"（2024年6月21日中华人民共和国外交部令第8号公布，自2024年6月21日起施行）\n\n美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。依据《中华人民共和国反外国制裁法》第三条、第四条、第五条、第六条、第九条、第十五条规定，中方决定对洛克希德·马丁公司相关实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施：\n\n一、对洛克希德·马丁导弹系统集成实验室、洛克希德·马丁先进技术实验室、洛克希德·马丁风险投资公司等后附《反制清单》列明的实体，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对洛克希德·马丁公司董事长、总裁、首席执行官詹姆斯·泰克里特、首席运营官弗兰克·圣约翰、首席财务官杰西·马莱夫等后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产；禁止我国境内的组织、个人与其本人进行有关交易、合作等活动；不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年6月21日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年6月21日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/8> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"洛克希德·马丁先进技术实验室","cn:english_name":"Lockheed Martin Advanced Technology Laboratories"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/anti-sanction-list/8-lockheed-martin-ventures>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/8-lockheed-martin-ventures> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_anti_sanctions> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"asset_freeze","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Freeze all assets in China, including movable and immovable property and other types of assets","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"The US recently announced again the sale of weapons to China's Taiwan region, seriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US joint communiqués, seriously interfering in China's internal affairs, and seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-06-21","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "8-lockheed-martin-ventures" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"关于对洛克希德·马丁公司实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施的决定","url":"https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zfxxgk_674865/gknrlb/fzcqdcs/202406/t20240621_11439508.shtml","publish_date":"2024-06-21","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs-order","document_id":"第8号","signatory":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","authority":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","content":"（2024年6月21日中华人民共和国外交部令第8号公布，自2024年6月21日起施行）\n\n美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。依据《中华人民共和国反外国制裁法》第三条、第四条、第五条、第六条、第九条、第十五条规定，中方决定对洛克希德·马丁公司相关实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施：\n\n一、对洛克希德·马丁导弹系统集成实验室、洛克希德·马丁先进技术实验室、洛克希德·马丁风险投资公司等后附《反制清单》列明的实体，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对洛克希德·马丁公司董事长、总裁、首席执行官詹姆斯·泰克里特、首席运营官弗兰克·圣约翰、首席财务官杰西·马莱夫等后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产；禁止我国境内的组织、个人与其本人进行有关交易、合作等活动；不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年6月21日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年6月21日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/8> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"洛克希德·马丁风险投资公司","cn:english_name":"Lockheed Martin Ventures"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/anti-sanction-list/8-james-donald-taiclet>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/8-james-donald-taiclet> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_anti_sanctions> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"asset_freeze","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Freeze all assets in China, including movable and immovable property and other types of assets","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_transactions","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止我国境内的组织、个人与其本人进行有关交易、合作等活动","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit organizations and individuals in China from engaging in transactions, cooperation or related activities with the entity","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"visa_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Visa ban and entry prohibition (including Hong Kong and Macao)","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"The US recently announced again the sale of weapons to China's Taiwan region, seriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US joint communiqués, seriously interfering in China's internal affairs, and seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-06-21","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "8-james-donald-taiclet" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"关于对洛克希德·马丁公司实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施的决定","url":"https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zfxxgk_674865/gknrlb/fzcqdcs/202406/t20240621_11439508.shtml","publish_date":"2024-06-21","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs-order","document_id":"第8号","signatory":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","authority":"cn/ministry-of-foreign-affairs","content":"（2024年6月21日中华人民共和国外交部令第8号公布，自2024年6月21日起施行）\n\n美国近日再次宣布向中国台湾地区出售武器，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。依据《中华人民共和国反外国制裁法》第三条、第四条、第五条、第六条、第九条、第十五条规定，中方决定对洛克希德·马丁公司相关实体和高级管理人员采取反制措施：\n\n一、对洛克希德·马丁导弹系统集成实验室、洛克希德·马丁先进技术实验室、洛克希德·马丁风险投资公司等后附《反制清单》列明的实体，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产。\n\n二、对洛克希德·马丁公司董事长、总裁、首席执行官詹姆斯·泰克里特、首席运营官弗兰克·圣约翰、首席财务官杰西·马莱夫等后附《反制清单》列明的企业高级管理人员，冻结在我国境内的动产、不动产和其他各类财产；禁止我国境内的组织、个人与其本人进行有关交易、合作等活动；不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）。\n\n本决定自2024年6月21日起施行。\n\n附件：反制清单\n\n外交部\n2024年6月21日\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/8> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-anti-foreign-sanctions-law","articles":["第三条","第四条","第五条","第六条","第九条","第十五条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"anti_sanctions","cn:sanction_list":"反制裁清单","cn:chinese_name":"詹姆斯·泰克里特","cn:english_name":"James Donald Taiclet"}}""" .
