:"cn/ministry-of-commerce","authority":"cn/ministry-of-commerce","content":"根据《中华人民共和国出口管制法》和《中华人民共和国两用物项出口管制条例》等法律法规有关规定，为维护国家安全和利益，履行防扩散等国际义务，决定将三菱造船株式会社等参与提升日本军事实力的20家日本实体列入出口管制管控名单（见附件），并采取以下措施：\n\n一、禁止出口经营者向上述20家实体出口两用物项，禁止境外组织和个人将原产于中华人民共和国的两用物项转移或提供给上述20家实体；正在开展的相关活动应当立即停止。\n二、特殊情况下确需出口的，出口经营者应当向商务部提出申请。\n\n本公告自公布之日起正式实施。\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/202611> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-export-control-law","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/mofcom-dual-use-export-control-regulation","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"export_control","cn:sanction_list":"出口管制管控名单","cn:chinese_name":"日本宇宙航空研究开发机构","cn:english_name":"Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/unreliable-entity-list/20231-lockheed-martin-corporation>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/20231-lockheed-martin-corporation> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_unreliable_entity> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_import_export","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit import and export activities related to China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_investment_new","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit new investment activities in China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"entry_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Entry ban for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"visa_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留以及居留资格","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Visa ban and cancellation of work permit, stay and residence qualifications in China for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"fine","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"对上述企业分别处以罚款，金额为《不可靠实体清单规定》实施以来各企业对台军售合同金额的两倍。上述企业应当自本公告公布之日起15日内，按照相关法律法规办理缴款。若逾期不履行本决定，不可靠实体清单工作机制将依法采取加处罚款等措施。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Impose fines on the above companies, with the amount being twice the contract amount of arms sales to Taiwan region since the implementation of the Unreliable Entity List Provisions. The above companies should complete the payment in accordance with relevant laws and regulations within 15 days from the date of this announcement. If they fail to comply with this decision within the time limit, the Unreliable Entity List Provisions Mechanism will take additional measures such as imposing additional fines in accordance with the law.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"参与对台湾地区军售","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Participating in arms sales to Taiwan region","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2023-02-16","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "20231-lockheed-martin-corporation" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"不可靠实体清单工作机制关于将洛克希德·马丁公司、雷神导弹与防务公司列入不可靠实体清单的公告","url":"https://www.mofcom.gov.cn/zwgk/zcfb/art/2023/art_123456.html","publish_date":"2023-02-16","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism-announcement","document_id":"〔2023〕1号","signatory":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-commerce-industry-security-and-import-export-control","authority":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","content":"为维护国家主权、安全和发展利益，根据《中华人民共和国对外贸易法》《中华人民共和国国家安全法》等有关法律，不可靠实体清单工作机制依据《不可靠实体清单规定》第二条、第八条和第十条等有关规定，决定将参与对台湾地区军售的洛克希德·马丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corporation）、雷神导弹与防务公司（Raytheon Missiles & Defense）列入不可靠实体清单，并采取以下处理措施：\n\n一、禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动；\n二、禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资；\n三、禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境；\n四、不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留以及居留资格；\n五、对上述企业分别处以罚款，金额为《不可靠实体清单规定》实施以来各企业对台军售合同金额的两倍。上述企业应当自本公告公布之日起15日内，按照相关法律法规办理缴款。若逾期不履行本决定，不可靠实体清单工作机制将依法采取加处罚款等措施。\n\n本公告未尽事宜，按《不可靠实体清单规定》执行。\n本公告自公布之日起实施。\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/20231> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-foreign-trade-law-2025","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-national-security-law-2015","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/mofcom-unreliable-entity-list-provisions","articles":["第二条","第八条","第十条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"unreliable_entity","cn:sanction_list":"不可靠实体清单","cn:chinese_name":"洛克希德·马丁公司","cn:english_name":"Lockheed Martin Corporation"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/unreliable-entity-list/20231-raytheon-missiles-defense>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/20231-raytheon-missiles-defense> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_unreliable_entity> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_import_export","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit import and export activities related to China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_investment_new","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit new investment activities in China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"entry_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Entry ban for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"visa_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留以及居留资格","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Visa ban and cancellation of work permit, stay and residence qualifications in China for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"fine","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"对上述企业分别处以罚款，金额为《不可靠实体清单规定》实施以来各企业对台军售合同金额的两倍。上述企业应当自本公告公布之日起15日内，按照相关法律法规办理缴款。若逾期不履行本决定，不可靠实体清单工作机制将依法采取加处罚款等措施。","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Impose fines on the above companies, with the amount being twice the contract amount of arms sales to Taiwan region since the implementation of the Unreliable Entity List Provisions. The above companies should complete the payment in accordance with relevant laws and regulations within 15 days from the date of this announcement. If they fail to comply with this decision within the time limit, the Unreliable Entity List Provisions Mechanism will take additional measures such as imposing additional fines in accordance with the law.","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"参与对台湾地区军售","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Participating in arms sales to Taiwan region","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2023-02-16","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "20231-raytheon-missiles-defense" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"不可靠实体清单工作机制关于将洛克希德·马丁公司、雷神导弹与防务公司列入不可靠实体清单的公告","url":"https://www.mofcom.gov.cn/zwgk/zcfb/art/2023/art_123456.html","publish_date":"2023-02-16","publish_time":"17:00","document_type":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism-announcement","document_id":"〔2023〕1号","signatory":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-commerce-industry-security-and-import-export-control","authority":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","content":"为维护国家主权、安全和发展利益，根据《中华人民共和国对外贸易法》《中华人民共和国国家安全法》等有关法律，不可靠实体清单工作机制依据《不可靠实体清单规定》第二条、第八条和第十条等有关规定，决定将参与对台湾地区军售的洛克希德·马丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corporation）、雷神导弹与防务公司（Raytheon Missiles & Defense）列入不可靠实体清单，并采取以下处理措施：\n\n一、禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动；\n二、禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资；\n三、禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境；\n四、不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留以及居留资格；\n五、对上述企业分别处以罚款，金额为《不可靠实体清单规定》实施以来各企业对台军售合同金额的两倍。上述企业应当自本公告公布之日起15日内，按照相关法律法规办理缴款。若逾期不履行本决定，不可靠实体清单工作机制将依法采取加处罚款等措施。\n\n本公告未尽事宜，按《不可靠实体清单规定》执行。\n本公告自公布之日起实施。\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/20231> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-foreign-trade-law-2025","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-national-security-law-2015","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/mofcom-unreliable-entity-list-provisions","articles":["第二条","第八条","第十条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"unreliable_entity","cn:sanction_list":"不可靠实体清单","cn:chinese_name":"雷神导弹与防务公司","cn:english_name":"Raytheon Missiles & Defense"}}""" .
<https://www.ammitto.org/entry/cn/unreliable-entity-list/20241-general-atomics-aeronautical-sy>
  ammitto:entity_id <https://www.ammitto.org/entity/cn/20241-general-atomics-aeronautical-sy> ;\n  ammitto:hasAuthority <https://www.ammitto.org/authority/cn> ;\n  ammitto:hasRegime <https://www.ammitto.org/regime/cn_unreliable_entity> ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_import_export","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit import and export activities related to China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"prohibit_investment_new","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Prohibit new investment activities in China","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"entry_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Entry ban for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasEffect """{"effect_type":"visa_ban","scope":"full","description":[{"value":"不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留以及居留资格","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Visa ban and cancellation of work permit, stay and residence qualifications in China for senior executives","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasReason """{"category":"other","description":[{"value":"参与对台湾地区军售","lang":"zh","script":"Hani","is_primary":true},{"value":"Participating in arms sales to Taiwan region","lang":"en","script":"Latn","is_primary":false}]}""" ;\n  ammitto:hasPeriod """{"effective_date":"2024-05-20","is_indefinite":false}""" ;\n  ammitto:status "active" ;\n  ammitto:reference_number "20241-general-atomics-aeronautical-sy" ;\n  ammitto:announcement """{"title":"不可靠实体清单工作机制关于对通用原子航空系统公司等三家美国企业采取不可靠实体清单措施的公告","url":"https://aqygzj.mofcom.gov.cn/flzc/gzjgfxwj/art/2024/art_e78af9c314b2466daa7f96b49766a158.html","publish_date":"2024-05-20","publish_time":"09:00","document_type":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism-announcement","document_id":"〔2024〕1号","signatory":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","publisher":"cn/ministry-of-commerce-industry-security-and-import-export-control","authority":"cn/unreliable-entity-list-working-mechanism","content":"为维护国家主权、安全和发展利益，根据《中华人民共和国对外贸易法》《中华人民共和国国家安全法》等有关法律，不可靠实体清单工作机制依据《不可靠实体清单规定》第二条、第八条和第十条等有关规定，决定将参与对台湾地区军售的美国通用原子航空系统公司（General Atomics Aeronautical Systems）、美国通用动力陆地系统公司（General Dynamics Land Systems）列入不可靠实体清单，并采取以下处理措施：\n\n（一）禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动；\n（二）禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资；\n（三）禁止上述企业高级管理人员入境；\n（四）不批准并取消上述企业高级管理人员在中国境内工作许可、停留或者居留资格。\n\n本公告未尽事宜，按《不可靠实体清单规定》执行。\n本公告自公布之日起实施。\n","language":"zh-CN"}""" ;\n  ammitto:group_id <https://www.ammitto.org/group/cn/20241> ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-foreign-trade-law-2025","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/npc-national-security-law-2015","citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:legal_citations """{"legal_instrument_id":"https://www.ammitto.org/legal-instrument/cn/mofcom-unreliable-entity-list-provisions","articles":["第二条","第八条","第十条"],"citation_type":"legal_basis"}""" ;\n  ammitto:raw_source_data """{"source_format":"yaml","source_specific_fields":{"cn:list_type":"unreliable_entity","cn:sanction_list":"不可靠实体清单","cn:chinese_name":"通用原子航空系统公司","cn:english_name":"General Atomics Aeronautical Systems"}}""" .
